<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { margin:0; padding:20px 0; background:#f0f4f8; font-family:'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color:#1f2937; }
    .container { max-width:540px; margin:0 auto; background:#ffffff; border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background:#0f2d5e; padding:32px 40px; text-align:center; }
    .header .icon { font-size:44px; display:block; margin-bottom:12px; }
    .header h1 { color:#ffffff; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; margin:0; }
    .header p  { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size:13px; margin:5px 0 0; }
    .body { padding:40px; }
    .body p { font-size:15px; color:#374151; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:16px; }
    .warning-box { background:#fef2f2; border:1px solid #fecaca; border-radius:10px; padding:16px 20px; margin:20px 0; font-size:13px; color:#991b1b; line-height:1.6; }
    .warning-box strong { display:block; margin-bottom:4px; color:#7f1d1d; }
    .cta { text-align:center; margin:28px 0 12px; }
    .cta a { display:inline-block; background:#1a56db; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; padding:16px 44px; border-radius:10px; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; }
    .fallback { background:#f9fafb; border-radius:8px; padding:14px 18px; margin-top:20px; }
    .fallback p { font-size:13px; color:#6b7280; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .fallback .url { font-family:monospace; font-size:12px; color:#374151; word-break:break-all; background:#e5e7eb; padding:8px 12px; border-radius:4px; display:block; }
    .security-note { font-size:13px; color:#9ca3af; border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb; padding-top:20px; margin-top:24px; line-height:1.65; }
    .footer { background:#f4f6f9; padding:20px 40px; text-align:center; font-size:12px; color:#9ca3af; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <span class="icon">🔑</span>
      <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
      <p>{{institution_name}} &mdash; Powered by FuhsoX</p>
    </div>

    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi <strong>{{user_name}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>We received a request to reset the password for your FuhsoX account. Click the button below to create a new password:</p>

      <div class="cta">
        <a href="{{reset_link}}">Reset My Password</a>
      </div>

      <div class="warning-box">
        <strong>⏰ This link expires in {{expiry_minutes}} minutes.</strong>
        If you don't reset your password within this time, you'll need to request a new link.
      </div>

      <div class="fallback">
        <p>If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <span class="url">{{reset_link}}</span>
      </div>

      <div class="security-note">
        🔒 <strong>Didn't request this?</strong> If you didn't ask to reset your password, you can safely ignore this email.
        Your password will remain unchanged. If you're concerned about your account security, please contact your institution's FuhsoX administrator.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} {{institution_name}} &middot; Powered by FuhsoX
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
